## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-197">异步搜索可以显示结果，如同时搜索其他结果时可以找到这些标识符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-197">An asynchronous search can show results as they are found while simultaneously searching for additional results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-198">这可用于任务，例如填充列表框。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-198">This is useful for tasks such as populating list boxes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-199">此属性的默认设置为 `false`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-199">The default setting for this property is `false`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-200">下面的 C# 示例演示如何创建的异步搜索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-200">The following C# example shows how to create an asynchronous search.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
//Set the Asynchronous property to true.  
src.Asynchronous = true;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-204">此属性设置为该属性必须是可分辨的名称属性，例如成员或受。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-204">The attribute that this property is set to must be a distinguished name attribute, such as member or managedBy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-205">该属性可以是单个或多个值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-205">The attribute can be either single or multi-valued.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-206">有关详细信息，请参阅 adschema 主题"[成员](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_member.asp)"和"[托管由](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_managedby.asp)"在 MSDN 库中[ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-206">For more information, see the adschema topics "[Member](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_member.asp)" and "[Managed-By](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_managedby.asp)" in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-207">按照由基对象的属性中指定的可分辨名称标识的对象执行搜索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-207">The search is performed against the objects that are identified by the distinguished name that is specified in the attribute of the base object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-208">例如，如果基对象是一个 adschema 组类和<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>设置为"成员"，则将针对是组的成员的所有对象执行搜索。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-208">For example, if the base object is an adschema group class and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> is set to "member," then the search will be performed against all objects that are members of the group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-209">有关详细信息，请参阅在 MSDN 库中的"组"类主题 adschema [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-209">For more information, see the adschema "Group" class topic in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-210">当<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>使用属性，<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A>属性必须设置为<xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-210">When the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property is used, the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property must be set to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-211">如果<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A>属性设置为任何其他值，设置<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>属性将引发<xref:System.ArgumentException>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-211">If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property is set to any other value, setting the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property will throw an <xref:System.ArgumentException>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-212">有关详细信息，请参阅在 MSDN 库中的"执行属性范围查询"主题[ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library))。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-212">For more information, see the "Performing an Attribute Scope Query" topic in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-213">下面的示例演示如何使用<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>与要获取组的成员的成员属性的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-213">The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property with the member attribute to get the members of a group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-214">然后打印的成员和他们的电话号码的第一个和最后一个名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-214">It then prints out the first and last names of the members and their telephone numbers.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
DirectoryEntry group = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=MyGroup, …");  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher(group "(&(objectClass=user)(objectCategory=Person))");  
src.AttributeScopedQuery = "member";  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("sn");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("givenName");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("telephoneNumber");  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll())  
{  
    Console.WriteLine("…");  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-232">下面的 C# 示例演示如何设置<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A>属性<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always>，以便它取消引用别名，当同时搜索次级和查找基对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-232">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> property to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> , so that it dereferences aliases when both searching subordinates and locating base objects.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
// Set DerefAlias to Always.  
src.DerefAlias = DerefenceAlias.Always;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-242">下面的示例演示如何以十六进制格式返回可分辨名称的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-242">The following example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-303">如果<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A>为空引用 (`Nothing`在 Visual Basic 中)，搜索根设置为当前使用你的服务器的域的根。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-303">If <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), the search root is set to the root of the domain that your server is currently using.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-304">有几种方法可以在全局编录搜索：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-304">There are several ways to search in the global catalog:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-305">枚举全局编录和选取的第一个子级。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-305">Enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-306">指定服务器名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-306">Specify the server name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-307">使用 dsgetdcname 发现函数查找全局编录。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-307">Use the DsGetDcName function to find the global catalog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-308">有关 dsgetdcname 发现函数的详细信息，请参阅主题"dsgetdcname 发现"MSDN 库中[ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-308">For more information on the DsGetDcName function, see the topic "DsGetDcName" in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-309">获取全局目录的根 Dse 并询问"rootNamingContext"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-309">Get the RootDSE  of the global catalog and ask for "rootNamingContext".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-310">使用全局编录，就像使用 LDAP 指定的搜索路径。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-310">Use the global catalog, specifying a search path as if using LDAP.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-311">例如，"GC: / / OU =...，DC =...，DC =..."。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-311">For example, "GC://OU=..., DC=..., DC=...".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-312">下面的 C# 代码演示如何枚举全局编录和选取的第一个子级。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-312">The following C# code shows how to enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
    ```csharp  
    DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("GC://forestname");  
    IEnumerator ie = entry.Children.GetEnumerator();  
    ie.MoveNext();  
    entry = (DirectoryEntry)ie.Current;  
    DirectorySearcher search = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
    ```

  
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.SecurityMasks = SecurityMasks.Dacl | SecurityMasks.Owner;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="32ce9-350">下面的 C# 示例演示如何设置<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A>属性`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32ce9-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
